      "date": "2013-01-10 18:14:14.000000000",
      "message": "Patch Set 2: I would prefer that you didn't submit this\n\n> +#ifdef EXT3_EXT_CACHE_EXTENT\n\nIt would be good to add a short comment with the kernel version in which this is removed, so that it is easier to know when the code can be removed. \n> +        if (cex->ec_type == EXT3_EXT_CACHE_EXTENT)\n> +#else\n> +        if (!cex->ec_len && !cex->ec_start)\n\n(style) since ec_len and ec_start are not boolean values, please use:\n\n        if (cex->ec_len == 0 && cex->ec_start == 0)\n\n> +#endif",
